title: For Sale:  1911
postcontent: Gentlemen if you have not been paying attention as of July 1st we cant sale or trade firearms with each other in Colorado unless we visit a participating FFL to handle the transfer.  That alone changes the market on Armslist dramatically.  The fact you have to walk into a gunshop sucks but since you do why dont you realize Sellers that gun dealers  are selling your Glock , M&P , 1911 cheaper than you are here.  So sellers I know it sucks , but keep in mind your loaded 1911 can be had for much less than you are asking for here.  If you sale a  pistol or rifle with mags that carry 15 rounds or more they cant legally come with the firearm. I hate the laws, however  I certainly dont want us to loose armlist or hurt the cause to ovrrturn this nonsense.  So in closing lets price things fairly and carefully.  We can still trade , but of  course that has to be done at an FFL. If you guys know of FFLs that will help us through this garbage please share. But folks be aware the gungrabbers are out there so be careful and dont shoot yourselves in the foot.  I miss trading on my off time on Armslist, hopefully will be doing this again soon.

title: For Sale/Trade:  Highly Modded Glock 34
postcontent: I am selling a highly modded G34 as the title says. The slide has been cnc'd, with two large side windows, and the front of the slide has been milled on the bottom into an angle which takes away the blocky look.  The frame has been stippled, trigger guard has double undercut and trigger guard also slightly rounded.  The backstrap angle has been slightly reduced as well.  The slide has been drilled and tapped up top and a Burris Fastfire II is mounted directly to the slide.  The barrel is a match lone wolf 6-port.  Trigger is the zev-tech fulcrum trigger, which is adjustable for over and pretravel.  The striker has been replaced with a polished striker and safety plunger has been replaced with a polished titanium plunger.  All springs have been replaced dropping the trigger pull to an average of 3.5lbs.  The gun will come with several diff springs an connectors so you can adjust the weight as you like.  The plastic captured guide rod has been replaced with a tungsten non-captured guide rod which was cut to length since the front of the slide has been milled.  Several different weight recoil springs will be included as well.  The gun currently has a 13lb spring installed.  Gun was cerakoted back to black after machine work, the fulcrum trigger is black with a red safety.  The recoil spring is red as well which gives the gun just enough of a second color to contrast well.  Ejector and extractor have both been upgraded.  Extractor was replaced with a hardened piece and ejector is a zev-tech hardened titanium ejector.  Bottom of grip is fitted with 6oz backstrap plug mated to a polished dawson ice magwell.  I think that is everything that has been done or added.  It would cost approx. $2,500.00 to build this gun which is roughly what I have invested.  I am only selling to fund another similar project to a long slide M&P.  I have a glock 20 and 32 that are modded similar as well and are a blast to shoot like this 34.  Gun will come with 2 17rnd mags and 1 33 round mag.  I placed a feeler ad a couple months ago for $2300.00 and I know that is a insane amount of money for a Glock but I have spent a insane amount of money to build this pistol.  I got alot of interest before and thought I had it sold a couple of times but at the last minute the people couldnt come up with the funds.  I had prob 100 people text mke wanting more pictures and asking a thousand questions.  I ask that people only contact me who have a serious interest in buying the gun.  I am lowering price to a more realistic $1200, which yes is still insane, but almost a $1000.00 loss and about all of the loss I am willing to take.  Email replys dont work well for me so I ask anyone to TEXT, 704-902-NINE-TWO-EIGHT-ZERO, who is interested and wants more pics.  Would also consider selling the slide by itself or trading just the slide.  Thanks for looking!! No Shipping
